text: Liang Soon Hin (born 13 February 1944) is a Malaysian wrestler. He competed in the men's freestyle flyweight at the 1964 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1944 births Category:Living people Category:Malaysian male sport wrestlers Category:Olympic wrestlers of Malaysia Category:Wrestlers at the 1964 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
